{
  "stem": "27351.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was at 10 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they told us to march, six of us in a row.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The place was illuminated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was 10 o'clock in the evening, but it was bright, bright light.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this time, in this selection, there were the the werkschutz the people that were guarding us in the camp, who took part in it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the foreman, the German foreman, the civilian workers, who worked for this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as we were marching through, of course, my mother, after the death of her son, was ruined.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was-- there were three people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was the fourth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was the fifth, I believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, I, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a moment, just one moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother was pulled out by a-- by a civilian foreman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was pulled out, and I ran after her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't think at that point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- It was just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I just ran after my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We were collected at the site, and the group was getting bigger and bigger-- older people, some children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my mother despairing that I was there, and why did I come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were put in some little-- I believe it was a little factory hall-- until the entire group was collected, the selection was finished.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then we were led out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And as we stood there, I thought, it was close to a wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was sure that they are going to shoot us there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Somehow I-- all the werkschutz people were there with their-- with their machine guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I thought, that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's strange, because I remember having some amazing clarity of mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
